    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756750/extras/0822732a7bbd22feeb4ad578706b7496.avif?t=1765995982\" width=1280 height=350 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《赫拉多尼亚》是一款心理恐怖游戏。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>故事</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >朱莉娅是一位普通的女性，她与丈夫和女儿居住在赫拉多尼亚市。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一天，她回到家，发现丈夫出城工作，而家里被翻了个底朝天。于是，朱莉娅踏上了一段寻找女儿的旅程，这段旅程将迫使她面对自己最大的秘密——那些她竭力隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756750/extras/a9528235427a5deb36425da2bbeb82dc.webp?t=1765995982\" width=1280 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>亮点</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第一人称恐怖：</strong>扮演朱莉娅，一位与丈夫和女儿住在赫拉多尼亚市的普通女性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>环境：</strong>赫拉多尼亚的世界背景设定在2005年左右。探索城市环境，如学校和市医院。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756750/extras/a9528235427a5deb36425da2bbeb82dc.webp?t=1765995982\" width=1280 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>玩法</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >物品收集</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解谜</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756750/extras/a9528235427a5deb36425da2bbeb82dc.webp?t=1765995982\" width=1280 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
